Go through the Directory structure of the application.
Create following endpoints 
a) GET :- localhost ..../client/sum/101/102 :- endpoint returns the sum of two number (101+102 = 203)
Read about @PathVariable
b) GET :- localhost ..../client/addition?number1=101&number2=102 :- endpoint returns the sum of two number (101+102 = 203)
Read about @RequestParam

 
